{
  "stem": "210.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he always put me on the list but he-- you know, but he always did.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, he says, tomorrow morning, instead of coming here, you go to my house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he lived in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's like in the suburb.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I would go there, and I would stay there, let's say, two days, three days.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I-- you know, he had a garden.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They called it [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I worked over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when the time-- you know, two, three days went by, when it was already-- when all these people already sent away and, you know, things.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they took away the the-- when you were on the list, they took away your ration cards.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you had nothing to eat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I came back, you know, when it was quieted down, he told me that it's OK for me to come back to the-- to the shop to work.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And on the way there, I was-- you know, we were going in a-- in a-- not-- it wasn't a bus.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was like a trolley.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I was on the trolley to go to, to work, and they took everybody off the trolley and me too.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they put us on a place where there was a big, big, like a empty place.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they usually-- they called it the potato-- the potato plaza.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not plaza, you know, Platz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they took me there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from there, they took everybody out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I saw some people there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were guarding us, this Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I saw somebody that's always used to come into the office where I used to work.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
